⚠️ Demographic Mismatch Detected ⚠️

The Lab Order demographic details do not match the Account details:
{!form_txtMismatchedValues}

🔹 Account Information
   - Name: {!$Record.Opportunity.Account.FirstName} {!$Record.Opportunity.Account.LastName}
   - Gender: {!$Record.Opportunity.Account.Gender__c}
   - Date of Birth: {!$Record.Opportunity.Account.DateOfBirth__c}

🔹 Lab Order Information
   - Name: {!Get_Lab_Order.First_Name__c} {!Get_Lab_Order.First_Name__c}
   - Gender: {!Get_Lab_Order.Gender__c}
   - Date of Birth: {!Get_Lab_Order.Date_of_Birth__c}

Please reach out to the patient if you need to confirm their demographic information.
To make corrections and re-submit the order, click "Update Order" at the top of the Lab Order page to enter the updated details.
